        {
            "id": "s_l2_1",
            "type": "text",
            "title": "Two Roads 🛤️",
            "content": "There are two main ways to create variables in modern JS:\n\n1. `let`: Use this if the value might **change** later.\n2. `const`: Use this if the value **never changes** (constant)."
        },
        {
            "id": "s_l2_2",
