        },
        {
            "id": "s_l2_3",
            "type": "code",
            "title": "Reassigning 🔄",
            "content": "With `let`, you can give the box a new value.",
            "codeSnippet": "let score = 0;\nscore = 10; // Change to 10\nconsole.log(score);",
            "codeLanguage": "javascript",
            "canRunCode": true
        },
        {
            "id": "s_l2_4",
            "type": "code",
            "title": "CONSTant 🛑",
            "content": "With `const`, once you set it, it's set forever.\n\nTrying to change it will cause an error (red text)!",
            "codeSnippet": "const pi = 3.14;\n// pi = 5; // Error!",
            "codeLanguage": "javascript",
            "canRunCode": true
